  "detailed_description": "Fractal Fury is a third person online shooter with strategic dismemberment. Free to play for up to 16 players online or locally.<br> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100% free without microtransactions or pay-to-win of any kind.<br></li><li> Multiplayer and single-player with horde game mode.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISMEMBERMENT SYSTEM</h2><br>Shoot your opponents hands off to make them harmless.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/de2cf252211ce6dd179775f95f829cad.poster.avif?t=1617527295\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/de2cf252211ce6dd179775f95f829cad.webm?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/de2cf252211ce6dd179775f95f829cad.mp4?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Shoot their legs off to immobilise them<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/323b9749f794b1f16ada2ce5201d45eb.poster.avif?t=1617527295\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/323b9749f794b1f16ada2ce5201d45eb.webm?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/323b9749f794b1f16ada2ce5201d45eb.mp4?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Shoot in a torso to destroy enemies armor and shoot in a core to destroy your enemy. <br>Or extract a core and use it to repair yourself or to crete an energy shield<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/f1668fde04fb428e7957879dac534561.poster.avif?t=1617527295\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/f1668fde04fb428e7957879dac534561.webm?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/f1668fde04fb428e7957879dac534561.mp4?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is also single player with hordes of zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/26ed569b94370f1b73d8e34d8d7d680e.poster.avif?t=1617527295\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/26ed569b94370f1b73d8e34d8d7d680e.webm?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1417490/extras/26ed569b94370f1b73d8e34d8d7d680e.mp4?t=1617527295\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME MODES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Team Deathmatch – classic team deathmatch.<br></li><li> Capture The Flag – kill all enemy team or capture the enemy flag and bring it to your base to win a round.<br></li><li> Hardcore – very fast and tough sort of battle royale game mode. Small map, 4 minutes per round. Last alive player wins the round.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OTHER FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Players can host servers.<br></li><li> LAN support.<br></li><li> Single player with horde game mode.</li></ul>",
